Package com.isbx.androidtools.networking

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UploadManager.SuffixRule
    An interface for generating a string suffix to be appended to an uploaded file name given a Uri for the original file and an index for the file's position in the current upload request queue.
    UploadManager.UploadListener
    A listener interface to receive completion, error, and progress events during an upload request
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    UploadManager
    This class provides a simple interface for uploading an arbitrary number of files to Amazon S3.
    UploadManager.IndexedSuffixRule
    An implementation of UploadManager.SuffixRule that maps an array of suffixes to the files being uploaded.
